Package agh.alleviation.model

Class Ticket

java.lang.Object
agh.alleviation.model.Ticket
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable
@Entity
public class Ticket
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Externalizable
Class responsible for representation of a ticket. It keeps the information about the seance and its price. Seance's price may be different from the ticket's price, as a customer may have a discount.
Author:
Ksenia Fiodarava
See Also:
Seance, Serialized Form
